<html>
    <head>
        <title>Ebill batch mailer - mail client setup</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    </head>
    <body>
        <h3>Mail client setup</h3>
        <p>
            For each mail server:
        </p>
        <ol>
            <li>
                Copy X.509 file
                <blockquote>
                    /etc/pki/dovecot/certs/dovecot.pem
                </blockquote>
                from dovecot server to mail client machine
            </li>
            <li>
                Import to java keystore:
                <blockquote>keytool -importcert -file ${filename}.pem -alias ${alias} -keystore ebillcerts</blockquote>
                Example:
                <blockquote>keytool -importcert -file www.ebill.dovecot.pem -alias www.ebill.co.il-1 -keystore ebillcerts</blockquote>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p>
            Remark: status updater launch script should contain this code:
            <strong>
                -Djavax.net.ssl.trustStore=/path/to/ebillcerts
            </strong>
        </p>
    </body>
</html>
